Chi Limited Marketing Director, Mrs. Toyin Nnodi, has said the ongoing campaign by Chivita titled: “Everyone has a Chivita” was created to boost its market share. The campaign, which started March 8, is already raising consumer consciousness to Chivita’s various offerings and reinforcing its category leadership in Juices, nectar and still drinks. Nnodi said Chivita is committed to innovation, prioritizing consumers’ expectations including need for health, nutrition and refreshment with best quality juices. “In essence, whether the occasion calls for indulgent taste, distinctive refreshment, rejuvenation, enablement for active health or preference for fruit juice made from natural ingredients with no artificial colour, preservatives and flavours, there is a Chivita to guarantee satisfaction,” she said.   Complete abandoned school project, old students’ beg…     EKSU, Alumni announces endowment prize     CCECC to partner Lagos on housing development   Nnodi explained that Chivita comes in exciting variants and varying pack sizes. She said: “Everyone has a Chivita campaign is to remind consumers of the high quality, nourishing and fruity goodness that the innovative Chivita brand provides to meet their varying needs.” Known for its high quality, health and nutrition, Chivita includes Chivita 100%, Chivita Active, Chi Exotic Nectar, Happy Hour by Chivita, Chivita Ice Tea and very recently, Chivita Smart Malt Drink – which is uniquely positioned to give children all the energy they require to learn and play. Chi Exotic variants are a range of rich, unique fruity blends that offer irresistible taste and distinctive nourishment, making it ideal for indulgence and relaxation. Happy Hour by Chivita is rated the fastest growing juice brand with innovative variants that keep consumers refreshed. while Chivita Ice Tea is the perfect beverage for rejuvenation and provides valuable nutrients required by the body.